Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:32.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}我什么也不怕 我爱你 无法忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:41.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}风儿硬是拆开 我们缠绵甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:49.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}面对无法停止的炽热心动 请不要流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:57.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}令人无法讨厌的冷漠态度 见不到面令我痛苦万分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:05.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}你郁闷不乐的声音 令我心碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx80\1c&HFFE9EB&}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那块石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,算了,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从管理员室的壁橱里 找到的一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎么样的一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子拜托五代帮忙调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代事后得知这是惣一郎 送给响子唯一的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去拿那块石头 请你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#40 令人心酸的温柔 圣诞节是恋爱的预兆!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得派对是七点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝啊喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不到七点钟耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没到,不过就快七点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会是因为舍不得会费 而改变主意不来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的,他会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,先喝酒吧 老板,啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,喝吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从啤酒开始喝吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,等了很久吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下了很大的雪 可能会积雪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小余呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经先去饭店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经买好了,香槟也买了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝点什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝了,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(笨蛋)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去饭店租套房来开派对 也只有在这种时候能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大笨蛋)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,查出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,我要美式咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查是查出来了,可是那块石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了带来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在你的公寓吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么放在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘在电车里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛,只不过是一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢了一块石头就大惊小怪 也未免太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天我去找一块类似的给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,是啊是啊,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟之前,上行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在哪一带?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较后面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第几节车厢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛… 想一想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我记得住的话 就不会把东西忘在车上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是比较后面的车厢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说没有收到这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法,对吧 来,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上,30分钟前的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快从东京车站折回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去搭下行的列车找找看 或许也是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8号月台下行列车快进站了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在架子上,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是这个位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为商店就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,你去看后面的车厢 我去看前面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,大家喝个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸转到我这边来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟三鹰在一起 可以玩跟五代不能玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,接个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为出了一点差错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚一点才会到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不太确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请这样转告给管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她就行了,是吧 好,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有人担心你,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,下一班电车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一点差错?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不晓得是什么事 他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我拜托五代一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是因为这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿到了,新宿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块石头有这么重要吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我不重要 但是对管理员很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,你少开玩笑了 你少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混帐,你有在听吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再去车站办公室问问看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已有人捡到送过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们走了没多久,我就接到联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说现在在东京车站保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿喔 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 为什么石头变成椅子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那位老爹讲话有点口音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然白跑了一趟 不过,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能做的都已经做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你一起去向她道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,拉着你到处跑 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请我吃顿午餐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是开玩笑的啦 不要发这么大的火嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为有人会把它捡去 失物招领处,或许太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不相干的人来说 跟垃圾没啥两样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成是我的话,就算捡到了 也会立刻扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,不要这样 大家都在看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!找到了吗?太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太好了 走,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的包包!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车!我买的圣诞礼物!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒楣透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,一起来跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你这个受欢迎的 竟然独占朱美,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是…不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛一个人在那里 扮演忧愁寡妇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为五代不在的关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把三鹰分一半给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来跟我们一起喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们继续玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,那我们继续跳罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么,又是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,我打电话来问的包包呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位旅客捡到送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 现在在四谷车站保管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了,好烫 冷死了,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车怎么还不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜托你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没力气去四谷车站领了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天我再去你家拿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面没有放 立刻需要用到的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是不要去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不要这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴脸舞时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定时间 然后把店内的电灯关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠圣诞树的灯光来跳舞 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好主意 我去跟老板说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你没事吧? 小心嫁不出去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不是那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,真讨厌 只是接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是茶茶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?片山先生? 他今天没有来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,好,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是个很棒的礼物…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直这样塞下去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我在这里下车?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么咒语?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,制造气氛,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太,你不跳舞了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么我来跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代可能不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算来了也来不及了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,三鹰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么事都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在问什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么这么晚才来?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是跑到外面约会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,罚喝三杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的快把我们等死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的有在等我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有 还是熟悉的玩具最好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块石头是石灰岩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白点叫纺锤虫 听说是一种小虫的化石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约三亿年前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些一个一个的白点 都还是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么普通的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是个很棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不让你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真是爱乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你突然跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那块石头 是惣一郎送我的礼物是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是郁子告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你的时候 感觉心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道那块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我这么心跳不已的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我这么心跳不已的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不应该拜托你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么说才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧 好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜这张卡片的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们稍微绕远路回去,好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶,现在要预告下一回喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,好好地疯一疯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是大过年的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又很想泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:23:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.57,0:24:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“对出浴的响子心动 露天温泉的偷窥大赛”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:06.81,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:26.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}当我们互相凝视时 就会有一道奇妙的旋律 在心中回响着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:41.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}无法用言语来表达爱 只好弹奏起了钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:55.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}请把梦丢进来 为我测量一下 爱有多深
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:25:06.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}用轻触的嘴唇演奏着 平静的合声
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:21.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}即使拥抱着你依然惆怅满怀 梦见了Fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.06,0:25:33.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87\1c&HEBEBE4&}开启了只有我们两人 才看得见的门扉Fantasy

